        public void invoke(Aggregate aggregate,
                   com.google.protobuf.Message message)
        Invokes the applier method.

        The method delegates the invocation passing empty message as the context parameter because event appliers do not have a context parameter.

        Such redirection is correct because AbstractHandlerMethod.getParamCount() the number of parameters} is set to one during instance construction.
